{"tid":2319149,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港電台：丹麥為多年前從格陵蘭帶走兒童道歉","createTime":"2020-12-10T01:40:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T02:15:06.000Z","uid":290404,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9e2d23a8ad32e40fa5d9a18d23a797b5b20a7ef8","tid":2319149,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T01:40:02.000Z","msg":"一俾許智峯過黎丹麥，港台就搵野唱衰佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>丹麥政府為1950年代一項以格陵蘭島上兒童為對象的社會實驗，正式道歉。</strong><br />\n<br />\n當年有22名兒童從島上家庭被帶走，送到丹麥接受教育，希望返回格陵蘭後，作為模範推動社會發展，並加強兩地的文化聯繫，但實驗最終失敗收場。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>大部分兒童返回原居地之後，不少人因為忘記母語，而且與本身的文化斷裂，無法再融入社會，大部分人從此再無同家人見面。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564542-20201210.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564542-20201210.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYpjrpXFO54mr1mpDNnesGdkc%3D&h=d5aad95d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564542-20201210.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=82c6c8f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564542-20201210.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"2fe0f402820a86cf517ab5b554af536469958c3b","tid":2319149,"uid":290118,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T01:41:47.000Z","msg":"人哋肯認錯，都唔算唱衰啦？<br />\n你估偉大的中國，成日責任不在佢咩"},{"pid":"57ebdb8cf86641ae8a28ebe2e8cea6e19955ef4b","tid":2319149,"uid":57677,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T01:47:15.000Z","msg":"港台冇做錯,不過比狗咬緊"},{"pid":"38a4b92559d4f75de1b36584037a88c665cf0881","tid":2319149,"uid":22701,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T01:49:47.000Z","msg":"人地政府肯道歉，支那港共政府有道過歉？永遠錯在X方 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f608b003851982ec7360e222b833db146ec8926e","tid":2319149,"ui